snippet.textDisplay: Such a beautiful song ! The glass cage represents the standard of society and the soul is hidden inside.  The song thirsts for someone, a true love.  Everyday , see all kinds of couples walking side by side, wondering what kind of love is right for themselves.  I am a princess but I have to keep my eyes closed to the standard.  Pain poured down like water, hoping that someone could wipe away the tears on the glass.  Society is always harsh, the little girl standing silently in front the shop is also forced to follow the standard.  But in the end, someone came to break the glass - break the standard- discover your soul and accept who you are.  And Set you free  <3 ------ That was my opinion . Love you Sam Smith
